	<summary>
	10/19/1993--Introduced.
Amends the Outer Continental Shelf Lands Act to direct the Secretary of the Interior to transmit decisions approving certain offshore lease sales to the Governor of each affected State. Grants the States specified time after such notice to disapprove such decision.

	</summary>
